==习性与分布==
其[[习性|习性]]不明，可能分布于[[牙买加|牙买加]]的[[特里洛尼区|特里洛尼区]]<ref name=Extinction>{{cite web|title=Ara erythrocephala|url=http://www.petermaas.nl/extinct/speciesinfo/redheadedmacaw.htm|publisher=The Extinction Website|accessdate=22 January 2013|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20081013035627/http://www.petermaas.nl/extinct/speciesinfo/redheadedmacaw.htm|archivedate=2008年10月13日}}</ref>。唯一已知的是它们[[栖息|栖息]]在[[山|山]]上的[[森林|森林]]中<ref name=BirdLife>{{cite web|title=Jamaican Green-and-yellow Macaw Ara erythrocephala|url=http://www.birdlife.org/datazone/speciesfactsheet.php?id=30076|publisher=birdlife|accessdate=22 January 2013|archive-date=2016-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304040859/http://www.birdlife.org/datazone/speciesfactsheet.php?id=30076|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

